```{.r .cell-code}
library(ggplot2)
library(forcats)
```
:::



::: {.cell}

```{.r .cell-code}
qatar_cars <- qatarcars %>% 
  group_by(origin) %>% 
  mutate(n_cars = n())
```
:::



::: {.cell}

```{.r .cell-code}
qatar_cars %>% 
  ggplot() + 
  geom_bar(aes(y = reorder(origin, n_cars), fill = enginetype), position = 'dodge') +
  scale_fill_viridis_d(option = "turbo") +
  labs(title = "Cars Produced by Country", x = "", y = "", fill = "Engine Type") +
  theme_minimal() + 
  theme(panel.grid.minor = element_blank(),
        panel.grid.major.y = element_blank())
```
